{"word":"ἀμφίαλος","slug":"ἀμφίαλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμφίαλος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἅλς</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>sea-girt</i>, of islands, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of Corinth, <i>between two seas</i>, Horace's <i>bimaris</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}